title: [SOLVED] Elemtalist lux out of hextech chest
body: So I recently just got Elemtalist lux and I was able to actually get enough essence but I didn't get any icons that usually come with skin is that normal?

replies.body: Yeeeeaaaa so getting that skin and redeeming it from Hextech won't actually give you any of the associated icons =\ . I'm curious as to which one you were looking forward to getting though!
